{"tid":1627720,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"我地應該搞返「購買日」","createTime":"2019-10-05T17:21:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T06:24:20.000Z","uid":33709,"like":104,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"0096fc475f8973c091a1a028d9bad4880f0bb1f3","tid":1627720,"uid":33709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:21:09.000Z","msg":"林鄭搞緊急法 再叫黨鐵全日停駛 商場唔開 <br />\n就係想制造係我地破壞左經濟 令商家受損<br />\n<br />\n「購買日」就係要用銀紙去話俾社會、藍絲、中立聽 其實唔係我地破壞經濟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢一日我地瘋狂去幫襯「黃店」、用銀紙懲罰佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一日抽三四間出黎懲罰 條隊有幾長排幾長！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同時又可以建立黃絲經濟圈<br />\n<br />\n建議：可以係閒日返工時間一齊去 冇集會 冇抗爭就可以去<br />\n<br />\n手足平時爆鋪、燒野呢啲行動 和理非參與唔到<br />\n但係呢樣活動就連左膠都可以一齊參與<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人數大增、又合法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60d1425ac585b4d7df2b715ebb705c426dc7ce74","tid":1627720,"uid":33709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:21:24.000Z","msg":"推呀 用銀紙懲罰佢地呀"},{"pid":"7b37f7efffd3e3122487a4273a4d6975c2ad3ef9","tid":1627720,"uid":33709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:22:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a04a3a0bec4a26da0e62fee7f54c26d09a1d3b27","tid":1627720,"uid":236281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:23:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tKjqaJY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtKjqaJY.jpg&h=3e00a1ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a618146df0ac07ea1391104a64d8cc63a12985b","tid":1627720,"uid":33709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sc